        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊]#为研究他喝下幽门螺杆菌培育汤#】巴里•马歇尔，幽门螺杆菌发现者。为了研究，他从病人身上取下幽门螺杆菌，培育后，将其与牛肉汤混合喝下，“以身试菌...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%96%9D%E4%B8%8B%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E6%B1%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%96%9D%E4%B8%8B%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E6%B1%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为研究他喝下幽门螺杆菌培育汤#</span></a>】巴里•马歇尔，幽门螺杆菌发现者。为了研究，他从病人身上取下幽门螺杆菌，培育后，将其与牛肉汤混合喝下，“以身试菌”。马歇尔介绍，幽门螺杆菌像“魔术贴”一样紧贴在胃壁，很难去除，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%AA%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E7%BA%AA%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年纪越大幽门螺杆菌带来的风险越大#</span></a>，如胃病和癌变。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4965225930358820" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hjltfppe3dj61ii0uoe8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kxgWBTLFlx089Y7CBx6U010